reviewText: What a snooze fest video!  No narration and nothing more than slow (and I mean VERY slow) moving videos and the island's scenery and not much at that.  A total waste of money.

This video nicely captures the beauty of the Kwajalein Atoll.

It will likely be of interest primarily to persons who have lived at or have visited the atoll.  Having lived there for over 11 years this video is a welcome addition to our video library.

-
Unbelievable views of the most beautiful water I've ever seen. Would be amazing to actually live there and experience day to day... If you can, pour yourself a cocktail & watch this from your hammock, then relax in paradise. Next best thing to being there!
